Package Implementation

Class Inventory

java.lang.Object
Implementation.DataManager
Implementation.Inventory
Direct Known Subclasses:
Store
public class Inventory extends Implementation.DataManager
The Inventory class extends DataManager to provide methods for retrieving and updating inventory data from a CSV file. This class manages player inventory, including item ID, item name, quantity, and category.
